# llms.txt Sync Check

After any change to API endpoints, services, pricing, request/response formats, or payment configuration, you MUST review and update `frontend/public/llms.txt` to keep it accurate.

## Checklist

- All API endpoints listed with correct HTTP methods and paths
- Service names, descriptions, and pricing match the code
- Request input fields and response output format (including the `{ serviceId, output }` wrapper) are correct
- Payment flow description matches actual x402 middleware behavior
- No hardcoded values that should be dynamic (e.g., supported networks come from config)

## Key source files to cross-reference

- `src/app.ts` — route definitions
- `src/agentServices.ts` — service catalog, pricing, schemas
- `src/perplexitySearch.ts` — search service implementation
- `src/x402Middleware.ts` — payment middleware
